{
  "stem": "27285.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my mother-- and we were standing there in the rain, and looking around, because we didn't know exactly whom to go to.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But then we said, if somebody is going to talk German on the street, it must be Jews because it was a little Czech town [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So and that was it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they took us in, and fed us, and we could wash in warm water, [LAUGHS] and the next day we joined-- we went to Brno.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was like [INAUDIBLE] years or more, years ago, I think.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, no, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I only remember how important it was that [LAUGHS] you found somebody who wouldn't give you to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Definitely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we were already thrown out of school, they were already a few orders that we are not supposed to do, or yes, to do, or we could do.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Definitely--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it went so fast, it went so fast.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I did not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I only-- as the Germans were already in Vienna, it was-- you were not supposed to go on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was all those little things starting, making you feel humiliated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, as a child, I was 7, or 8, you don't get it, you have your own life, somehow, and you are protected by grown ups.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was-- later you reconstruct, but I don't want to say about this, because I want to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You wanted me to tell about what I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had youth certificates for the children, put us into a children's home, not yet an orphanage, and went on an illegal transport to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was too dangerous for children to take along.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody could predict what is more dangerous then.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
